public final class DynNetworkViewTask<T,C>
extends AbstractDynNetworkViewTask<T,C>

DynNetworkViewTask is the task that is responsible for updating the visualization of a dynamic network DynNetwork by updating the time. In order to increase speed performance, only elements that changed from the last visualization are updated (by interval tree search over all elements). The dynamics of the network is stored in DynNetwork, whereas the dynamics of the visualization is stored in DynLayout.

Author:
Sabina Sara Pfister
